              "chord": "",
              "text": "Deep within, my heart cries out to You,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Hungry and thirsty too"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For that sweet flow of life."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Shining One, in me direct Thy rays,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Shine through all false displays;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Let me not be deceived."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, I know, I need Thy light to shine."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How else can I be Thine?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You must enlighten me."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Cleanse me now; don’t let one sin remain."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I cannot be the same;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Your life is all I need."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh forgive my failure and my sin."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Make me so clean within"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So You can flow in me."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, the joy! To have that life and peace!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Darkness and death have ceased"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In Thy sweet presence, Lord."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, the joy from fellowship so real!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Even the heav’ns, I feel,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
